    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, B4, B5, C4, C5, 20 February 09:00 UTC to 21 February 12:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>A Polar Low is now at sea area C4, southwest of Bjornoya. It is moving northeast and is expected to weaken Monday afternoon at B5. Northeast severe gale 9 is expected on the west side of the Polar Low in B4, B5, C4 and possibly C5.</description>
